## Usage

### Global Options

| Option | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `--help` | Show help and exit |
| `--version` | Show version and exit |
{% if use_config_file %}
| `--config PATH` | Path to config file (default: `~/.config/{{ project_name }}/config.{{ config_format }}`) |
{% endif %}
| `--verbose` | Enable verbose output |
| `--quiet` | Suppress non-error output |
| `--no-color` | Disable colored output |

### Commands

#### `{{ project_name }} run`

Execute the primary action.

```bash
{{ project_name }} run [OPTIONS] [ARGS]...

Options:
  --dry-run   Show what would happen without making changes
  --output    Output format: text, json, yaml  [default: text]
  --help      Show this message and exit
```

#### `{{ project_name }} config`

{% if use_config_file %}
Manage tool configuration.

```bash
{{ project_name }} config show              # Print current config
{{ project_name }} config set KEY VALUE     # Set a config value
{{ project_name }} config get KEY           # Get a config value
{{ project_name }} config reset             # Reset to defaults
```
{% else %}
Show current configuration and environment.

```bash
{{ project_name }} config show
```
{% endif %}

